These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, may
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| Birthday   | may | december |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-2::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, tram
1. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
2. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2      |
| Transport   | airplane | tram |

 #################################

 
